    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我传你武功，到此为止，好在你有那册天下第一奇书《锁骨销魂天佛秘笈》，只要持之以恒，不断地练下去，你将来的成就，实可超出老夫之上，好了，我们缘尽于此，你出洞去口巴……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老前辈，你……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不用管我，只紧记报父仇不可鲁莽从事，加紧修练武功，多多结交天下英雄好汉，再把你父亲被害真相公布武林周知，至于……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "进去搜搜！进去！走……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "打！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "挥金入木",
